ght_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=yCTaMrpfOZ6CYUu1fmQGLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d7694f33\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=AU&amp;message=6180399&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a>"},{"pid":"65ec55f64cffb4795c70646dda999db168cf98d1","tid":598564,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"當忍屎成功忍到返屋企再爆出黎個下好有成就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中場波都冇咁開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf6a5eb9cba5679ebaef05c23cc1add73a0d7d6","tid":598564,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"從此之後我就戒左丁，每日不停咁忍屎，直到放工返到屋企先去。嗰種快感真係爽過打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}